				<td colspan="2"><span>2) Respawn is 13 hours I believe, long enough, but you could go in theory every day.
<br />

<br />
3) There are 2 mobs that death touch you. If you agro them in any way, you will get flattened. That means chain agro to. So if a mob wanders off that you have agro on, and gets near the DT golem, bam. Loading, Please Wait. FM should get you off any agro lists though, so as long as you're careful, you shouldn't die to DT. There's no maximum range on DT either, they can kill you from across the zone. </span></td>
